
This SubVersion repository is for the Open Language Archives Community

olac-admin@language-archives.org


Process for building new file releases:

1. Copy the latest dated version of xml file to a new dated xml file,
  then edit this file
2. Make the needed changes to the corresponding Makefile.
3. Commit these changes to Subversion and send SB email.
4. SB run the Makefile
5. SB commit the changes to Subversion.
6. SB rsync to the live web site.
